 Our analysis hints that the mean redshifts of the two highest tomographic bins are higher than initially estimated. In addition, a number of consistency tests are conducted to assess the robustness of our analysis. Comparing our result with Planck-2018 cosmic microwave background observations, we find a {\textasciitilde}\$2{\textbackslash}sigma\$ tension for the \${\textbackslash}Lambda\$CDM model.},
